com.ae2dms.model.gameObject.wall.WallObject.FloorUnit
public class FloorUnit extends WallObject
The FloorUnit class creates floor units to be used for the world. A floor unit is a unit shaped like a square that is treated as a floor, with collision on the top, left, and right sides. The floor collides with any kind of game object. When an enemy is bubbled, the enemy will still be stopped by a floor unit above it.
